<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Service</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(15, 87, 211, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .email-header {
       
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .email-header img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: start;
        }
        .email-body h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .email-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #9ab8d9;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .email-button:hover {
            background-color: #9292ab;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }
        .email-footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #c8cbcfb0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .email-footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        {{!-- <div class="email-header">
            <a href="https://ibb.co/w4DNCtL"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/Zxy6K9J/colorful-bird-illustration-gradient.png" alt="colorful-bird-illustration-gradient" border="0"></a>
            <h1>Welcome to Our Service</h1>
        </div> --}}
        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Hello {{username}},</h1>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us! We're thrilled to have you on board.</p>
            <p>To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="email-button">Verify Your Email</a>
            <p>If you didn't request this email, no action is needed—simply ignore it.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Your Company Team</p>
            <p>If you need any assistance, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@yourcompany.com">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            <p>© 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
